msgstr "轴心点模式"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/transform/transform_control/pivot_point/index.rst:20
msgid ""
"The pivot point is the point in space around which all rotations, scalings "
"and mirror transformations are centered. You can choose one of five *Pivot "
"Points* from a drop-down list in the header of any 3D area, as seen here in "
"(*Pivot Point modes*). The pages linked below describe each *Pivot Point* "
"mode in more detail."
msgstr ""
"轴心点处于全部旋转、全部缩放和全部镜像变换操作所围绕的中心位置。您可以在任何3D视图区域标题栏的 “轴心点模式” "
"下拉菜单中，选择五种常见模式中的一个。您要做的就是为您的工作选择最高效的类型去准确放置轴心点。 "

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/transform/transform_control/pivot_point/index.rst:36
msgid ""
"Note that even if the above examples use meshes, the same rules apply for "
"other types (curves, surfaces...) as well."
msgstr "请注意：虽然上面的例子中使用的是网格物体，也可以在其它类型的物体（曲线、表面……等）使用同样的规则。 "
